  "instructions": [
    "Heat the pork fat in a large stone bowl or skillet over medium-high heat",
    "Add the pork pieces and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent, about 3 minutes",
    "Add the yuzu juice, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine",
    "Reduce heat to medium-low and simmer, covered, for 20 minutes",
    "Stir in the chopped parsley and cook for an additional 2 minutes",
    "Serve hot, garnished with additional parsley if desired"
